    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/5ebd2e1d74f234d55e9581fde14bf8f5.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以体验故事、解谜以及与怪物的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/1207b9c7d8a1452445624ec9818dc218.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/4cad9d2c15169f6b5ced35e502f1f99f.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/13800da92c7c160f2035ca175b7e382c.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1080 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丽莎有一天在一座别墅中醒来时已经失去了记忆。在那座地方，她与家人和朋友们相遇并逐渐找回了记忆。在这个过程中，她开始意识到自己似乎与其他人不太一样......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/324d70d26f219c2df653c0fc0117a4c4.avif?t=1764856832\" width=606 height=307 /></span>                    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/13800da92c7c160f2035ca175b7e382c.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1080 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解开谜题后，可以打开被堵住的道路，或者获得能够开启门的钥匙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/cfd50b0f034f92541e4ed8b9348eea50.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/b688a0c05874f2f673c5a5f3160e0ef0.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/339f91d9de5d67132a2d26184f31b6b1.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1080 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用武器击败那些阻碍你前进的怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/45771ad02c9ce72f9726913086b0116b.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/2b16f1a5d2c852727e1d17c44489e61e.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
